<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; color: #444; }
        .container { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 5px; }
        .header { color: #6c5ce7; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .button { background: #6c5ce7; color: #ffffff !important; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">Lunara AI</div>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>You requested a password reset. Please click the button below to set a new password. This link will expire in 1 hour.</p>
        <p>
            <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
        </p>
        <p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <br>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Lunara AI Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
